<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Beautiful Background Homepage</title>
  <style>
    /* Set background gradient */
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff8a00, #e52e71);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    /* Optional: Add additional styling for the content */
    .content {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .content h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .content p {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="content" style="display: flexbox; background-color: #e52e71; color: white; font-weight: bolder; font-size: larger;">
    <h1>Welcome to the E-Commerce Admin Products CRUD API (Website) Dashboard/Panel</h1>
    <p>Do anything beauty with the products in the E-Commerce Inventory!</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
